short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Check the score of your Azuki collection easily.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Chrome extension is designed to simplify the process of checking scores for Azuki, Elemental, and Beanz. Whether you're a collector or simply curious about the scores of these collectibles, This extension makes it effortless to access this information right from your browser.

Effortless Score Checking: With a single click, you can instantly retrieve the scores for Azuki, Elemental, and Beanz collectibles without leaving your current tab.
User-Friendly Interface: Our extension offers a user-friendly interface that seamlessly integrates into your Chrome browser.
Real-Time Updates: Stay up-to-date with real-time score information, ensuring you always have the latest data at your fingertips.
Privacy-Focused: We respect your privacy and only access the necessary data for score retrieval. Your browsing experience remains secure and private.
